{"tid":1596791,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［行動討論］9.30搞三罷想令香港變死城根本冇可能成功","createTime":"2019-09-26T15:58:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T05:01:29.000Z","uid":213747,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5611e1004fe2d87731f8eb0df50492d011599549","tid":1596791,"uid":213747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:58:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>想要一個成功嘅三罷就要有目標</strong></span><br />\n我唔係話三罷會冇人參加 <br />\n而係三罷縮喺屋企唔會令香港變死城<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">想要證據？<br />\n你聽晚行落自己屋企附近嘅m記或者吉野家就睇到</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n咁應該做啲咩好？<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>我建議9.30搞個香港清潔日</ins></span></strong><br />\n當日沿用最近有手足提議嘅五區集會地點集合<br />\n然後一齊行去鬧市見到支那旗就拆 太高就用漆彈掉<br />\n仲有見到賀支那國慶嘅banner都拆<br />\n賀佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位手足點睇"},{"pid":"5542425a046f93dce31722a1f5dbcdbd1827d630","tid":1596791,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:59:34.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n[文宣] 我哋好似忘記咗其中一條重要戰線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592692</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7b0f04508ca4a254d7e3fe1cca2a7f8f6a870b1c","tid":1596791,"uid":155674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:01:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民反DQ 一個不能少</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1596375/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1596375/page/1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">不如就喺十月一號嘅土共生日，香港人不分和理勇、不分界別、不分範籌好似之前個別請攬炒巴，前線，醫護咁。一次過請哂所界別既人上去民間記者會</span>"},{"pid":"c6911cc1fa3e6744c4a47f03584c49a102c1237b","tid":1596791,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:04:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f61c8e935aab546bf79bf2232dfeffa2982dba1f","tid":1596791,"uid":213747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":